# 3D Printing Shop Event Website

A simple and responsive event website created using **HTML** and **CSS** for a 3D Printing Shop Event.

## Features

* Event banner image
* Promotional video and intro audio
* Event registration form
* Responsive and clean design

## Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3

## How to Run

Open `index.html` in any web browser.

## Purpose

This project is created for learning and demonstration of basic front-end web development.
